{"type": "article", "id": 13715, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-08-19T08:09:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 266, "name": "椅子"}, {"id": 5554, "name": "支架"}, {"id": 2737, "name": "猫桌"}, {"id": 1492, "name": "钱包"}, {"id": 4216, "name": "植物"}, {"id": 12527, "name": "收纳"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607133848u6yhKD5BGTxWQOz4.png", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tCaTable 2.0 by LYCS\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是一款来自 LYCS 零壹城市建筑事务所的猫桌，他们曾经在去年推出<a href=\"http://lycs-arc.com/archives/3759\" target=\"_blank\">猫桌 1.0</a>，广受好评。今年的“进阶版”不再是一个四平八稳的桌子，而是一个有着巧妙的镂空设计的立方体，不管从哪一个角度看过去，喵星人都可以找到一个玩耍的方式。同时，小方块组合在一起，可以演变出各种形态的架子，在给猫营造一个生活空间的同时，也可以放置别的物品。<a href=\"http://lycs-arc.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看 LYCS 零壹城市建筑事务所的更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111227OrS1Zovq4LsBgi2m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68854167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021112275xPnHChNYf2Ugzue.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111228pcrs0IFzk8MGvTDu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.42291667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111229l5CM6LuJYaki9zds.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111229d6L7aAzgGEtkfK81.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111230m12LcaTHbudPDiW4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111230YS8ilz5gtsaHVJKI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tSimplify by Groupwork \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>墨尔本设计工作室 Groupwork 推出了一款名为 “Simplify” 的浴室收纳架，包括毛巾悬挂处，肥皂托盘，小物件收纳盒，牙刷和刷子放置处，以及纸巾悬挂处。和它的名字一样，产品的设计非常简单明晰，但在细节上非常充实和体贴，考虑到浴室各种常见的物品，并集中在简洁的一条横梁之上。同时，金色和木质棕色的搭配看上去和谐而明快，是件能给沐浴带来好心情的产品。产品可以组合使用，也可以拆分来依照需求购买。<a href=\"http://www.groupworkstudio.com/#intro\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>查看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111231abGvSque1Lh0mRIj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111231z1X5iK6eCRuIfw30.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111232tmAWEs9zNcQiUKwH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111232Xs4VInHc3z2htbaP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111233oTv7LjB625VRh8mI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111233rQInvDUczSCTsg4M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111233diyDGTsKxw0o5rbU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tDesk Collection by Maderacraft\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是 Maderacraft 推出的一套苹果产品的支架，包括 iMac，iPhone，iPad，蓝牙键盘，名片的支架，这些支架的材料是竹子，而竹子们来自 Maderacraft 专门为商业种植的可再生的环保竹子，让用户在摸到最大自然的产品的同时，避免了对资源的过度消耗。这套产品简单而又优雅，对于全套苹果设备的用户来说，是个不小的诱惑吧。<a href=\"http://maderacraft.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111234o5SkMgKnhj1VRIc7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111235MdOUKxN5Xplf9hCG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111235CLUyOGIkilP9YDNx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111235oUgzQym0CVTHnJba.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021112361Mnl8oQBRzx6tEpc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111237SfxsJPU7T4zMwNDe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111237DsSaRx6TiHjtZJCQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111238vNoM8C5zw4g9qPU3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141434hv0x4UGYls7QwWbV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141435UamtvdODIwMHpscg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tVerdure by Seoyeonjin Choi\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>“Verdure” 是一个自动的植物栽培和灌溉装置，你只需要撒播种子，它便可以自行生长，自动浇水，甚至主动为自己获得光照。更重要的是，装置的底部是一个小凹槽，里面有一把小剪刀——你可以随时剪下植物来食用。你大概要问这是什么食物了，有些人爱极了但有些人觉得不可思议，这里面种植的是香菜。当然了，你也完全可以自己尝试种点儿什么别的。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111238S2vs7t6Mf3UOR1JI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111239S7HPDChrK6dIopXF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111239DGrNeV4itYblS1xJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.47142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111240oEIMZNYqsB43DPW1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.39904762\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111240frgY0sxAIZ8Bo5DT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tDouble Zero by David Adjaye\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>圆形控们看过来，David Adjaye 新设计的这一系列椅子叫做 “Double Zero ”，椅背和椅面全部是五颜六色的圆，同时，椅子的框架系统也不像普通的椅子那样是四条腿儿，而是选择了交叉的支撑结构，加上圆形的椅背和椅面，整个椅子不管从哪个角度看过去都个性十足。<a href=\"http://www.adjaye.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看  David Adjaye 官方主页。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111241wcjVCIFS1a0DmEdJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89364303\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111241YRGgFPr0qVS63mxz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89364303\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111241fiyao0EqTMHKx6jc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74694377\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111242GSvRAXa4Y58VUel6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74694377\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111242ces8H7qLjaln2K3V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86919315\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021112432Nrsx7fXuZIv1m0j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89364303\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111243zVrlkQO9h4imBYRp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89364303\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111244PZ7Xvw1598HpBoEl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86430318\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111244Pxpe7uB2jZGrIUWc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86430318\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111245G7kE9rJhRQDyzonp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tSlim 2 Wallet by The Supr Good Co\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>来自美国明尼苏达州的 The Supr Good Co 一直以极简设计为主打，最近他们推出了一款名为 Slim 2 wallet 的小钱包，采用光滑的皮革，外部除其 Logo 外再无其他装饰，内部则采用了弹力带来稳定卡和现金，适合放在大口袋里面作为分层收纳使用。钱包目前有棕色，深灰色和浅灰色三种颜色可以选择，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/supr/slim-2-the-perfect-minimal-wallet\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。<a href=\"http://www.suprgood.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看 The Supr Good Co 的官方主页，了解他们更多产品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111245rY36aA7nyKXDT4Zh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111245nKIf0BONLCwcqtAa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111246uxhbG0Tvs6gkW5lQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111246k2I6SogBVC4LmpPT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03235294\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111247rYmCQfTnWG5EVoaO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111247OCWpzt5lQFRKM0D4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.28970588\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111248tN29OKWlMQdwSL83.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111248DkpOy2YfrxgW4ea6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141435GkcSdl1JuroE8qMW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111250tcB5OJZ1eb3IALYi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111250ZmQ3JGsfEI0HTuLa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111250UC71IArSeQgBDcOb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71029412\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}